@DATABASE "Magnetron"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Magnetron"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                                 Magnetron
                                 =========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42671,235) ZXAMPoke(42672,160)"}          42671,235:42672,160

                         I'm pretty sure this infinite lives POKE works. All
                         it does is stop the game jumping to the Game Over
                         sequence, and you end up getting transported to
                         another place. I can't really play the game that
                         well, so I haven't been able to bug-test it (like
                         making sure none of your work is undone).
                         If it works, cool. If not, don't blame me.. I didn't
                         crack it, OK?!
                                          Rastan.
@endnode
